19
00:01:50,700 --> 00:01:54,700
Within this military camp, whose position is the highest?

20
00:01:58,400 --> 00:02:00,400
Bao Zitou, you answer.

21
00:02:02,800 --> 00:02:04,400
It's...

22
00:02:04,400 --> 00:02:06,600
Ah, it's the general!

23
00:02:06,600 --> 00:02:09,200
What did I tell you back then?

24
00:02:10,100 --> 00:02:12,200
Back then...

25
00:02:12,200 --> 00:02:17,800
Lord Military Inspector, your position is the highest here.

26
00:02:17,800 --> 00:02:20,200
There's no need to make things hard on my subordinates.

27
00:02:21,800 --> 00:02:24,620
Who are you?

28
00:02:27,800 --> 00:02:31,600
I am Lord Yongning, Chu Xiuming.

29
00:02:37,600 --> 00:02:40,150
Oh, so you are Chu Xiuming?

30
00:02:41,850 --> 00:02:44,790
My official position as the Military Inspector

31
00:02:45,620 --> 00:02:48,220
should be a grade higher than yours, right?

32
00:02:52,300 --> 00:02:53,900
Precisely.

33
00:02:53,900 --> 00:02:57,000
Since my position is higher than yours,

34
00:02:57,000 --> 00:02:59,800
why do you disrespect us?

35
00:03:00,900 --> 00:03:03,200
I am not sure what you are referring to.

36
00:03:03,200 --> 00:03:04,800
I am confused.

37
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:08,800
My Lord, if I treated you badly just now, please be forgiving.

38
00:03:10,400 --> 00:03:14,800
I came here by an imperial court order.

39
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:17,400
It was such a long and rough journey.

40
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:22,100
Why haven't I even been given a cup of tea?

41
00:03:22,100 --> 00:03:26,000
This is a military camp. We don't have as many supplies as other places.

42
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:29,200
Our soldiers fight to protect the country.

43
00:03:29,200 --> 00:03:31,300
We dare not lust after small pleasures.

44
00:03:31,300 --> 00:03:35,600
The soldiers usually live on plain water and simple congee.

45
00:03:35,600 --> 00:03:36,800
What do you mean?

46
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:38,700
Plain water and simple congee?

47
00:03:38,700 --> 00:03:41,500
Then, what have your military funds been used on?

48
00:03:43,600 --> 00:03:46,700
The Imperial Court has not given us funds in two years.

49
00:03:47,500 --> 00:03:49,000
In order to shoulder the concern of the Imperial Court,

50
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:53,800
after our soldiers finish training every day, they work on farmlands.

51
00:03:53,800 --> 00:03:58,300
We make all our own daily necessities.

52
00:04:00,500 --> 00:04:02,800
This is too much!

53
00:04:04,100 --> 00:04:06,100
Don't discuss political matters.

54
00:04:09,400 --> 00:04:11,000
All right!

55
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:13,600
I understand your suffering.

56
00:04:13,600 --> 00:04:17,900
To appreciate the soldier's hard work, I'll treat everyone to a banquet today.

57
00:04:17,900 --> 00:04:19,300
You cannot.

58
00:04:19,300 --> 00:04:21,500
The soldiers are used to eating like this.

59
00:04:21,500 --> 00:04:25,800
If they suddenly gorge themselves on rich food, I'm afraid they will get sick.

60
00:04:25,800 --> 00:04:27,400
Then they can at least drink alcohol, right?

61
00:04:27,400 --> 00:04:30,800
I want to drink with all the soldiers, can't I?

62
00:04:30,800 --> 00:04:32,000
Don't worry.

63
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:35,800
I will pay for everything today.

64
00:04:37,200 --> 00:04:38,400
It will have nothing to do with you.

65
00:04:38,400 --> 00:04:40,400
Alcohol is forbidden in a military camp.

66
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:44,000
I can't do this and I can't do that!

67
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:47,100
Is this how you treat the Military Inspector?  You're totally disregarding me!

68
00:04:47,100 --> 00:04:49,000
I do not dare.

69
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:51,000
There's nothing you don't dare to do!

70
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:52,800
You're working against me on purpose!

71
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:55,900
I will fire you today, do you believe me?

72
00:04:56,800 --> 00:04:58,600
Do you believe me?

73
00:05:04,300 --> 00:05:06,700
You don't believe it! I'll rip off your armor right now!

74
00:05:06,700 --> 00:05:07,600
- My Lady! 
 - Miss!

75
00:05:07,600 --> 00:05:08,690
- My Lady, calm down! 
 - Let me go!

76
00:05:08,690 --> 00:05:10,600
Let me go!

77
00:05:10,600 --> 00:05:12,700
- My Lady! 
 - Let me go!

78
00:05:12,700 --> 00:05:14,470
- My Lady! 
 <i> - Don't touch me!</i>

79
00:05:14,470 --> 00:05:15,700
<i>- My Lady! 
 - Miss!</i>

80
00:05:15,700 --> 00:05:17,600
<i>-My Lady! 
 - Miss! 
 - Let me go!</i>

81
00:05:17,600 --> 00:05:21,400
That Chu Xiuming! He really lives up to his title of a general.

82
00:05:21,400 --> 00:05:23,700
It's fine if he disrespected me in the past,

83
00:05:23,700 --> 00:05:27,500
but I'm the Military Inspector now and he still ignores me!

84
00:05:27,500 --> 00:05:30,800
No, I cannot accept this!

85
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:35,400
The trouble he's created for me now, I'll have him repay it ten times over!

86
00:05:35,400 --> 00:05:39,400
I will have him understand what "Hell hath no fury like a woman scorned" means!

87
00:05:39,400 --> 00:05:43,400
And she is petty as expected.

88
00:05:43,400 --> 00:05:45,600
Cut the crap!  Hurry and think of a plan!

89
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:48,200
I must beat that Chu Xiuming!

90
00:05:48,200 --> 00:05:52,200
It looks like you have a held grudge against Chu Xiuming for a while.

91
00:05:52,200 --> 00:05:55,200
Grudge? It's vengeance!

92
00:05:56,300 --> 00:06:00,100
Let me tell you. Do you know what "Two hearts are not one" means?

93
00:06:00,100 --> 00:06:02,590
What "It's hard to come to an agreement, return to our original paths" means?

94
00:06:02,590 --> 00:06:04,000
<i>(T/N: These are quoting the "Divorce Letter" Chu Xiumin wrote her)</i>

95
00:06:04,000 --> 00:06:06,200
What do they mean?

96
00:06:06,200 --> 00:06:10,600
Then do you know "Go our separate ways, both will find happiness"?

97
00:06:10,600 --> 00:06:14,200
He will be happy, but I won't be happy!

98
00:06:14,200 --> 00:06:18,000
These... should be words used in divorce letters.

99
00:06:19,600 --> 00:06:22,900
It's enough if you know about it. Don't talk about it.

100
00:06:22,900 --> 00:06:25,400
Yes, yes, yes, Lord Military Inspector.

101
00:06:25,400 --> 00:06:27,200
Why are you calling me by that title, too?

102
00:06:27,200 --> 00:06:30,000
Xiao Su, when did you become so polite with me?

103
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:32,400
But... I really never imagined it.

104
00:06:32,400 --> 00:06:36,500
The little brat from the past is an official now!

105
00:06:36,500 --> 00:06:37,900
It was just a coincidence.

106
00:06:37,900 --> 00:06:42,600
However, when I'm with you, Lord Jin, I will always be that little brother who scaled the walls and ripped off tiles with you.

107
00:06:42,600 --> 00:06:46,800
Xiao Su! You're awesome!

108
00:06:52,600 --> 00:06:54,600
You're awesome!

109
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:58,000
I never imagined it. You gave me a big gift as soon as we met up!

110
00:06:58,000 --> 00:07:00,700
I have a higher official position than Chu Xiuming!

111
00:07:00,700 --> 00:07:02,800
It's not a big deal.

112
00:07:02,800 --> 00:07:05,700
How is it not a big deal? I'm higher than him!

113
00:07:15,200 --> 00:07:20,400
Why did the emperor suddenly order the second miss of Rui Royal Manor to be a Military Inspector?

114
00:07:20,400 --> 00:07:23,200
I heard she was divorced by Chu Xiuming

115
00:07:23,200 --> 00:07:25,800
and fled from the manor in shame.

116
00:07:25,800 --> 00:07:28,200
If the emperor did this,

117
00:07:28,200 --> 00:07:33,000
he must suspect Chu Xiuming.

118
00:07:35,000 --> 00:07:38,200
We must make good use of this chance.

119
00:07:38,200 --> 00:07:41,700
The matter regarding the military pay, how has that been handled?

120
00:07:42,500 --> 00:07:46,200
Chu Xiuming is just a soldier. He hasn't received military funds for two years.

121
00:07:46,200 --> 00:07:48,700
He's brought the soldiers to cultivate land

122
00:07:48,700 --> 00:07:51,300
without a single complaint.

123
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:58,400
How about we use this chance to push the blame onto Chu Xiuming?

124
00:07:59,600 --> 00:08:02,400
Your words make sense, General Zuo!

125
00:08:03,000 --> 00:08:08,800
When that happens, the emperor will summon Chu Xiuming back to the capital for interrogation.

126
00:08:10,500 --> 00:08:13,600
After Chu Xiuming leaves his own territory,

127
00:08:14,500 --> 00:08:19,000
he will be like fish meat and we will be knives.

128
00:08:19,600 --> 00:08:23,300
At that time, attacking the imperial city...

129
00:08:23,300 --> 00:08:25,700
will be an easy task!

130
00:08:25,700 --> 00:08:27,700
Good!

131
00:08:27,700 --> 00:08:30,200
Lord Liu's strategy is brilliant!

132
00:08:30,200 --> 00:08:33,800
We will be eagerly expecting the future revolution!

133
00:08:50,800 --> 00:08:54,200
What's the logic behind letting Her Ladyship come to the frontlines as a Military Inspector?

134
00:08:54,200 --> 00:08:56,000
There must be something going on behind this.

135
00:08:56,000 --> 00:08:58,900
No matter what, it's good if Lady is back.

136
00:09:02,300 --> 00:09:06,100
Who knows what trouble she'll create coming back this time.

137
00:09:06,100 --> 00:09:07,800
Be careful, everyone.

138
00:09:07,800 --> 00:09:11,200
It seems like Lady has come for you, General.

139
00:09:11,200 --> 00:09:13,000
So what if she has?

140
00:09:13,000 --> 00:09:16,500
Please be careful and don't anger Our Lady.

141
00:09:16,500 --> 00:09:18,800
Or else, we'll be affected, too.

142
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:26,400
Did she bribe you two? You keep speaking up on her behalf!

143
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:29,200
- I do not dare! 
 - I do not dare!

144
00:09:31,500 --> 00:09:35,300
From now on, there is only the Military Inspector.

145
00:09:35,300 --> 00:09:37,400
There is no more lady.

146
00:09:50,700 --> 00:09:55,100
Military Inspector! The general requests an audience.

147
00:09:55,100 --> 00:09:56,800
I refuse!

148
00:09:58,900 --> 00:10:02,400
Rou Rou, you can take your leave. I want to speak to your mistress alone.

149
00:10:02,400 --> 00:10:04,200
Yes.

150
00:10:04,200 --> 00:10:06,200
What's wrong with you?

151
00:10:06,200 --> 00:10:08,100
You didn't hear what I said?

152
00:10:08,100 --> 00:10:11,100
Since you left, why did you return?

153
00:10:11,800 --> 00:10:16,200
I am a divorced wife. Where can I go?

154
00:10:16,200 --> 00:10:19,000
Chu Xiuming, I'd like to ask you.

155
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:23,200
Were you afraid I'd return or hoped I'd return?

156
00:10:26,600 --> 00:10:29,800
Even if you were returning, you shouldn't have returned with this identity.

157
00:10:29,800 --> 00:10:31,800
Then, what identity should I use?

158
00:10:31,800 --> 00:10:33,800
The general's wife?

159
00:10:33,800 --> 00:10:36,500
Or Second Miss of the Rui Royal Manor?

160
00:10:36,500 --> 00:10:40,000
I think being a military inspector is better.

161
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:42,400
Must you be like this?

162
00:10:42,400 --> 00:10:45,600
Starting from today, I will officially assume my position.

163
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:50,500
I will supervise everything in your military camp and your manor.

164
00:10:52,200 --> 00:10:55,900
Aren't you reaching a bit too far?

165
00:10:55,900 --> 00:11:00,000
How can I bother you with my manor?

166
00:11:00,000 --> 00:11:01,200
It's not a bother.

167
00:11:01,200 --> 00:11:05,000
I, the Military Inspector, am exactly someone who is this hardworking and loves being bothered about trivial matters.

168
00:11:05,000 --> 00:11:08,300
The general just needs to remember my military service.

169
00:11:09,600 --> 00:11:14,200
However, I've heard that a military command is unchangeable like a mountain.

170
00:11:14,200 --> 00:11:19,400
I don't know if the words of an official as high as me are effective.

171
00:11:19,400 --> 00:11:23,400
Can I order around the people in the camp?

172
00:11:23,400 --> 00:11:25,200
Since you were sent by imperial decree,

173
00:11:25,200 --> 00:11:28,300
everyone in the camp will listen to your orders.

174
00:11:28,300 --> 00:11:30,900
- Really? 
 - Really.

175
00:11:32,870 --> 00:11:36,390
Yesterday, I heard you say there was no tea in this military camp.

176
00:11:36,390 --> 00:11:40,550
I prepared some high-quality tea for myself.

177
00:11:40,550 --> 00:11:44,910
General, are you interested in having a taste?

178
00:12:04,330 --> 00:12:08,320
Military Inspector, have some tea.

179
00:12:25,080 --> 00:12:28,980
Military Inspector, please have some tea.

180
00:12:33,930 --> 00:12:35,750
Good, good.

181
00:12:35,750 --> 00:12:37,990
Since you are so courteous,

182
00:12:37,990 --> 00:12:40,210
then I will enjoy it.

183
00:12:43,880 --> 00:12:47,140
Chu Xiuming! Do you want to burn me to death? You did that on purpose!

184
00:12:47,140 --> 00:12:48,620
I wouldn't dare.

185
00:12:48,620 --> 00:12:50,410
This was your tea.

186
00:12:50,410 --> 00:12:52,970
I'm only presenting Buddha with flowers offered by someone else.

187
00:12:52,970 --> 00:12:54,610
You—

188
00:12:55,860 --> 00:12:57,930
Gather all the soldiers!

189
00:13:01,110 --> 00:13:03,390
I came here to supervise by imperial order.

190
00:13:03,390 --> 00:13:05,530
Some people may not like it.

191
00:13:05,530 --> 00:13:08,110
They think since I'm a woman,

192
00:13:08,110 --> 00:13:10,240
I cannot bear serious responsibilities.

193
00:13:10,240 --> 00:13:14,030
Today, I will compete with General Chu!

194
00:13:14,030 --> 00:13:16,760
All soldiers will bear witness!

195
00:13:18,900 --> 00:13:20,990
If Lord Military Inspector competes with me,

196
00:13:20,990 --> 00:13:22,730
I'm afraid it won't be fair.

197
00:13:22,730 --> 00:13:24,530
What wouldn't it be fair?

198
00:13:24,530 --> 00:13:26,080
Don't worry, General.

199
00:13:26,080 --> 00:13:29,030
You and I can shed off our status during the competition.

200
00:13:29,030 --> 00:13:32,080
We will compete as equals!

201
00:13:33,100 --> 00:13:35,450
Men and women are different.

202
00:13:35,450 --> 00:13:37,540
They differ greatly.

203
00:13:37,540 --> 00:13:40,100
You underestimate me, General!

204
00:13:40,100 --> 00:13:43,310
Even though I am a woman, I do not burden others with my responsibilities.

205
00:13:43,310 --> 00:13:47,060
Women can do just as well as men. General, just do your best.

206
00:13:47,060 --> 00:13:49,310
There's no need to go easy on me!

207
00:13:50,900 --> 00:13:51,970
Very well.

208
00:13:51,980 --> 00:13:54,680
Inspector, please pick your weapon first.

209
00:13:54,680 --> 00:13:56,480
Don't need weapons.

210
00:13:57,670 --> 00:14:00,040
Then you can make the first move.

211
00:14:00,040 --> 00:14:02,440
I didn't say we were having a physical fight either.

212
00:14:02,440 --> 00:14:05,970
Then, Lord Military Inspector, what do you want to compete with?

213
00:14:06,580 --> 00:14:09,100
What does Her Ladyship want to compete with?

214
00:14:12,010 --> 00:14:17,340
This competition tests the soldiers' ability to escape after being captured.

215
00:14:17,340 --> 00:14:21,770
After the competition begins, we will each hold a feather in our mouths and go underwater.

216
00:14:21,770 --> 00:14:25,470
Besides holding our breaths, we must undo the locks in time.

217
00:14:25,490 --> 00:14:28,320
The person who surfaces first will win.

218
00:14:29,260 --> 00:14:33,430
If anyone forfeits or encounters danger, they can spit out the feather.

219
00:14:33,430 --> 00:14:36,140
If either of you sees a feather float up to the surface,

220
00:14:36,140 --> 00:14:38,100
pull the chain and save the person below.

221
00:14:38,100 --> 00:14:39,620
It's that simple.

222
00:14:39,620 --> 00:14:41,850
General, do you have any objections?

223
00:14:41,850 --> 00:14:43,650
It's fine as long as the inspector is happy.

224
00:14:43,650 --> 00:14:46,260
General, in order to be fair,

225
00:14:46,260 --> 00:14:47,920
