257
00:17:58,880 --> 00:18:03,550
♫ <i> I wish to be your loyal servant </i> ♫

258
00:18:07,800 --> 00:18:11,280
Chu Xiuming! Did you go crazy or are you an idiot?

259
00:18:12,370 --> 00:18:15,280
Just treat me as going crazy or being an idiot.

260
00:18:15,280 --> 00:18:18,930
You could have forfeited, why did you have to do that?

261
00:18:18,930 --> 00:18:20,960
You were certain I would save you?

262
00:18:20,960 --> 00:18:24,680
You were certain I wouldn't abandon you?  Is that right?

263
00:18:25,940 --> 00:18:28,080
- Yes. 
 - You-!

264
00:18:30,080 --> 00:18:32,410
Chu Xiuming, let me ask you this.

265
00:18:32,410 --> 00:18:35,650
If I was the one in danger today, what would you have done?

266
00:18:35,650 --> 00:18:38,980
I would have done the same as you and try my hardest to save you.

267
00:18:39,530 --> 00:18:41,880
Then, why did you have to divorce me

268
00:18:41,880 --> 00:18:44,080
and insist on driving me away?

269
00:18:45,710 --> 00:18:50,790
Lord Inspector, it's not proper to discuss personal relationships here.

270
00:18:53,010 --> 00:18:55,110
Go back and rest.

271
00:18:55,810 --> 00:18:58,770
Chu Xiuming! You only know how to avoid the problem!

272
00:18:58,770 --> 00:19:01,110
When will you directly face your feelings?

273
00:19:01,110 --> 00:19:03,830
You clearly have love in your heart, but you won't admit it!

274
00:19:03,830 --> 00:19:07,810
Are you torturing me or yourself?

275
00:19:10,140 --> 00:19:13,230
If being with me brings so much pain to you,

276
00:19:13,230 --> 00:19:16,130
then you should leave quickly.

277
00:19:16,130 --> 00:19:18,080
If I could forget about you after I left,

278
00:19:18,080 --> 00:19:20,540
I wouldn't have returned!

279
00:19:37,280 --> 00:19:41,220
Since you're not willing to leave, then I'll go.

280
00:20:27,890 --> 00:20:31,550
Miss, do you want to eat something?

281
00:20:32,190 --> 00:20:35,260
Rou Rou, I want to drink alcohol.

282
00:20:35,260 --> 00:20:38,080
You can't! Alcohol is forbidden in camp.

283
00:20:38,710 --> 00:20:42,000
Why are you angering me just like Chu Xiuming?

284
00:20:42,000 --> 00:20:46,530
Now that you mention the general, I just heard the general returned to the manor.

285
00:20:48,500 --> 00:20:50,400
He can return to his manor.

286
00:20:50,400 --> 00:20:52,230
I'll stay in my camp.

287
00:20:52,230 --> 00:20:56,580
Since I became the Military Inspector, I shouldn't just vent my frustrations.

288
00:20:57,930 --> 00:20:59,860
Military affairs must come first.

289
00:20:59,860 --> 00:21:04,720
Miss, you're talking more and more like the general now.

290
00:21:04,720 --> 00:21:07,020
So what if I sound like him?

291
00:21:09,250 --> 00:21:12,640
That Chu Xiuming is intent on divorcing me.

292
00:21:12,650 --> 00:21:16,570
You said general wants to divorce you, but where is the divorce letter?

293
00:21:16,570 --> 00:21:18,170
I ripped it up!

294
00:21:18,170 --> 00:21:20,350
Who can prove that?

295
00:21:20,350 --> 00:21:22,590
I personally proved it, who else needs to prove it?

296
00:21:22,590 --> 00:21:25,660
I mean, you said the general divorced you,

297
00:21:25,660 --> 00:21:30,280
but you ripped up the divorce letter. Who can prove he divorced you?

298
00:21:30,970 --> 00:21:34,410
No— I did rip it up, but he can write another one!

299
00:21:34,410 --> 00:21:36,000
Then, you can rip it up again!

300
00:21:36,000 --> 00:21:37,220
Is there any use lying to myself like that?

301
00:21:37,220 --> 00:21:39,940
Then is there any use in lying to yourself, at all?

302
00:21:41,190 --> 00:21:45,700
Miss, I know you love the general and can't let him go.

303
00:21:45,700 --> 00:21:49,890
If you give up now, you will definitely regret it in the future.

304
00:21:49,900 --> 00:21:51,410
So get your spirits up!

305
00:21:51,410 --> 00:21:54,040
Even if you have to lie, you shouldn't lie to yourself!

306
00:21:54,040 --> 00:21:57,610
You have to "lie" the General back to your side!

307
00:22:00,330 --> 00:22:03,660
Then... how should I lie?

308
00:22:21,300 --> 00:22:22,740
<i>[Yongning Manor]</i>

309
00:22:22,740 --> 00:22:25,440
- My Lady! 
 - My Lady, you're back!

310
00:22:25,440 --> 00:22:28,330
- My Lady! 
 - My Lady, I heard you became Lord Military Inspector.

311
00:22:28,330 --> 00:22:30,370
Congratulations, Lady! Congratulations, Lady!

312
00:22:30,370 --> 00:22:31,400
Thank you.

313
00:22:31,400 --> 00:22:34,600
My Lady, you look so good in this armor.

314
00:22:34,600 --> 00:22:37,090
My Lady, when will you move back in here?

315
00:22:37,090 --> 00:22:39,790
If you don't come back, Xiao Cong will wither.

316
00:22:39,790 --> 00:22:42,450
That's right. The condition in the barracks is definitely worse than here at the manor.

317
00:22:42,450 --> 00:22:46,460
Come back more often, we'll make good food for you.

318
00:22:46,460 --> 00:22:47,940
Okay.

319
00:22:49,040 --> 00:22:50,220
The general...

320
00:22:50,220 --> 00:22:51,690
The general woke up early today.

321
00:22:51,690 --> 00:22:54,500
He's in the library dealing with official matters right now.

322
00:22:55,670 --> 00:22:59,310
Then prepare some food for me. I'll go find him later.

323
00:22:59,310 --> 00:23:01,040
And then we will eat a meal together.

324
00:23:01,040 --> 00:23:02,180
All right, great!

325
00:23:02,180 --> 00:23:03,370
Please, My Lady.

326
00:23:03,370 --> 00:23:06,610
<i>[Yongning Manor]</i>

327
00:23:14,620 --> 00:23:16,280
General.

328
00:23:46,030 --> 00:23:50,530
General, please go on with your duties, I won't bother you.

329
00:23:51,900 --> 00:23:56,360
I wouldn't dare to let Lord Inspector prepare the ink.

330
00:23:57,620 --> 00:24:03,100
In this general's manor, there is no military inspector, just your wife.

331
00:24:04,750 --> 00:24:07,340
But you and I are not married anymore.

332
00:24:08,230 --> 00:24:12,340
The divorce letter has already been destroyed, no one else knows about it.

333
00:24:12,340 --> 00:24:15,300
If General insists on divorcing me,

334
00:24:15,300 --> 00:24:19,370
then you should explain the reasons to the emperor. Right?

335
00:24:19,370 --> 00:24:20,980
Until then,

336
00:24:20,980 --> 00:24:25,600
General can you maintain the wedding status with me for the moment?

337
00:24:31,790 --> 00:24:34,940
All right. I'll oblige you for now.

338
00:24:34,940 --> 00:24:38,510
In front of other people, let's treat each other as spouses.

339
00:24:38,510 --> 00:24:42,650
But in the army camp, you're still my military inspector.

340
00:24:43,660 --> 00:24:45,310
All right.

341
00:24:46,030 --> 00:24:51,690
Now, no matter if it is a wife or military inspector,

342
00:24:51,690 --> 00:24:55,870
I'm earnestly requesting that you go back to the barracks.

343
00:24:55,870 --> 00:25:00,790
The army can't be one day without a general, nor can the army's matters be delayed

344
00:25:00,790 --> 00:25:03,430
because of our personal feelings.

345
00:25:04,860 --> 00:25:07,260
My Lady, do you mean it?

346
00:25:07,260 --> 00:25:11,530
Don't worry, I won't make trouble anymore.

347
00:25:11,530 --> 00:25:15,330
I want to help you handle the biggest and smallest matters of the army.

348
00:25:15,330 --> 00:25:17,950
I won't cause trouble.

349
00:25:17,950 --> 00:25:21,060
After all, protecting our homes and our country is a big responsibility.

350
00:25:21,060 --> 00:25:26,460
Both in public and private, I should be of some help.

351
00:25:26,460 --> 00:25:30,030
You need not worry about the affairs of the General's Manor,

352
00:25:30,030 --> 00:25:32,010
I will handle them accordingly.

353
00:25:32,010 --> 00:25:35,280
I won't let General worry about it.

354
00:25:38,470 --> 00:25:42,300
Good. Then let's go back immediately to the barracks.

355
00:25:42,300 --> 00:25:44,720
General, please wait.

356
00:25:44,720 --> 00:25:48,640
I had them prepare a meal already. Let's go back once we are done eating.

357
00:28:16,460 --> 00:28:19,960
<i>[Yongning Manor]</i>

358
00:28:36,920 --> 00:28:40,380
<i>[Yongning Manor]</i>

359
00:28:52,600 --> 00:28:54,170
This is for you.

360
00:28:55,170 --> 00:28:57,120
What is this?

361
00:28:57,120 --> 00:28:59,350
A pardon warrant.

362
00:28:59,350 --> 00:29:01,190
What's it for?

363
00:29:01,190 --> 00:29:04,030
In the barracks, military discipline is above all.

364
00:29:04,030 --> 00:29:07,710
If you act as you did before and violate the military rules,

365
00:29:07,710 --> 00:29:10,950
this badge can give you a pardon.

366
00:29:13,820 --> 00:29:17,000
Then I have to keep it safe. Thank you.

367
00:29:17,000 --> 00:29:18,580
You're welcome.

368
00:29:36,420 --> 00:29:38,320
Thank you.

369
00:31:15,120 --> 00:31:18,000
Stop right there! Stop!

370
00:31:23,750 --> 00:31:26,200
You all, the night is moonless and the wind blows hard,

371
00:31:26,200 --> 00:31:28,630
where are you going with these kids?

372
00:31:31,940 --> 00:31:36,220
I'd advise you to refrain from taking the side of an evildoer,

373
00:31:36,220 --> 00:31:38,020
free those kids now!

374
00:31:38,020 --> 00:31:39,530
Stop.

375
00:31:49,060 --> 00:31:50,570
General.

376
00:31:50,570 --> 00:31:53,250
- Leave. 
 - Yes, Sir!

377
00:31:53,250 --> 00:31:54,670
Let's go.

378
00:31:56,030 --> 00:31:57,400
Impudent.

379
00:32:04,700 --> 00:32:08,610
General, where are you sending these kids?

380
00:32:08,610 --> 00:32:10,050
Yama's palace? 
 <i>[Yama is the King of Hell]</i>

381
00:32:10,050 --> 00:32:12,400
These are my barracks.

382
00:32:12,400 --> 00:32:16,810
It's not your place as a little palace guard commander, to give orders.

383
00:32:16,810 --> 00:32:18,950
General, I wouldn't dare.

384
00:32:18,950 --> 00:32:23,070
How would I have enough free time to meddle in the general's affairs?

385
00:32:24,350 --> 00:32:26,600
I want to ask you...

386
00:32:26,600 --> 00:32:30,390
What is your purpose in being sneaky all day?

387
00:32:34,840 --> 00:32:39,240
The moon is beautiful tonight. I have a date with a beautiful lady.

388
00:32:40,920 --> 00:32:42,660
Farewell, General.

389
00:32:59,500 --> 00:33:01,230
<i>Lord Jin.</i>

390
00:33:02,180 --> 00:33:04,360
Lord Jin, did you want something?

391
00:33:04,360 --> 00:33:08,080
I brought back some dishes from the General's Manor. It'll improve your meal.

392
00:33:08,080 --> 00:33:11,430
Wow. Then I am gladly accepting the invitation.

393
00:33:11,430 --> 00:33:13,900
It's right there.

394
00:33:33,940 --> 00:33:34,980
General!

395
00:33:34,980 --> 00:33:37,920
Watch carefully that man named Xiao Su.

396
00:33:37,920 --> 00:33:40,460
General, are you speaking about that little palace guard next to the Military Inspector?

397
00:33:40,460 --> 00:33:41,490
That's right.

398
00:33:41,490 --> 00:33:43,450
What is suspicious about him?

399
00:33:52,460 --> 00:33:54,500
- Cheers! 
 - Cheers!

400
00:34:13,390 --> 00:34:15,300
Cautiously investigate that Xiao Su!

401
00:34:15,300 --> 00:34:17,440
If there's the slightest abnormal move, quickly report to me!

402
00:34:17,440 --> 00:34:19,120
Yes, Sir!

403
00:34:55,650 --> 00:34:58,250
<i>[Army Barracks - Restricted Area. Entry is forbidden.]</i>

404
00:34:58,250 --> 00:35:01,020
<i>[Those who violate this order will be punished.]</i>

405
00:35:44,190 --> 00:35:45,910
Have some tea.

406
00:35:53,660 --> 00:35:57,210
Rou Rou, have you seen Chu Xiuming and the others?

407
00:35:57,210 --> 00:35:59,040
No, I have not.

408
00:36:58,170 --> 00:37:01,770
Tell me. What exactly are you looking for?

409
00:37:02,400 --> 00:37:05,150
What's the matter, Great General Chu?

410
00:37:05,150 --> 00:37:08,910
Are you afraid that your innumerable crimes will be exposed by me?

411
00:37:09,620 --> 00:37:12,830
According to legend in the Imperial Court, Lord Yongning is a tyrant who doesn't know his limits,

412
00:37:12,830 --> 00:37:14,970
preys on the people, and brings calamity and chaos to the country.

413
00:37:14,970 --> 00:37:17,990
It looks like everything I've heard is true.

414
00:37:18,630 --> 00:37:22,830
It has always been beneath my dignity to be understood by people.

415
00:37:22,830 --> 00:37:24,870
Since you don't want to answer,

416
00:37:24,870 --> 00:37:26,670
let's just forget it.

417
00:37:30,330 --> 00:37:32,110
He trespassed in the army barracks, a restricted area.

418
00:37:32,110 --> 00:37:35,470
He will be punished according to martial law.

419
00:37:37,470 --> 00:37:40,470
He will be beaten to death with a staff.

420
00:37:40,470 --> 00:37:44,510
<i>Hold it! Stop it! Stop, stop, stop!</i>

421
00:37:44,510 --> 00:37:46,580
- Let me see who will dare to touch him! 
 - Move aside!

422
00:37:46,580 --> 00:37:48,270
<i>Su Su!</i>

423
00:37:48,990 --> 00:37:50,130
He's with me!

424
00:37:50,130 --> 00:37:51,840
Who dares touch him?

425
00:37:51,840 --> 00:37:53,780
How're you feeling? Are you hurt?

426
00:37:53,780 --> 00:37:55,460
He's with you?

427
00:38:02,310 --> 00:38:06,990
Lord Military Inspector, everyone is treated equally under martial law.

428
00:38:06,990 --> 00:38:09,110
This person trespassed in a restricted area.

429
00:38:09,110 --> 00:38:13,150
Even if you're a military inspector, you still cannot bend the law due to favoritism.

430
00:38:13,680 --> 00:38:16,660
I'm the Military Inspector, all of you have to listen to me.

431
00:38:16,660 --> 00:38:19,140
Besides, you should've clarified the situation before doing anything else.

432
00:38:19,140 --> 00:38:23,040
Just as you cannot be excessively tolerant toward villains, you also cannot kill good people unjustly.

433
00:38:31,650 --> 00:38:34,420
It should be fine if I use this to redeem Xiao Su's life, shouldn't it?

434
00:38:35,140 --> 00:38:37,470
You cannot go back on your word.

435
00:38:46,390 --> 00:38:49,740
I prepared this especially for you.

436
00:38:50,590 --> 00:38:53,030
You're actually using it to save his life?

437
00:38:54,650 --> 00:38:56,870
Since you already gifted it to me,

438
00:38:56,870 --> 00:39:00,130
then how I make use of it is of no consequence to you.

439
00:39:03,350 --> 00:39:07,220
In any case, no one is to harm Xiao Su today.

440
00:39:14,840 --> 00:39:16,570
Fine.

441
00:39:17,250 --> 00:39:19,310
I fulfill my promises.

442
00:39:19,870 --> 00:39:22,720
Since you're using the token to pardon him,

443
00:39:22,720 --> 00:39:25,020
he shall be pardoned.

444
00:39:25,020 --> 00:39:26,670
General!

445
00:39:44,300 --> 00:39:47,040
Su Su, are you all right?

446
00:39:47,040 --> 00:39:49,480
I'm fine. Thank you, Lord Jin.

447
00:39:54,000 --> 00:39:55,120
You've all arrived.

448
00:39:55,120 --> 00:39:56,410
- How many days have you gone without a bath? 
 - Have you been good?

449
00:39:56,410 --> 00:39:58,670
- You stink! 
 - Why are there children here?

450
00:39:58,670 --> 00:40:00,270
They are here due to the goodness of the general's heart.

451
00:40:00,270 --> 00:40:02,950
He took in the orphaned children of the rebel army and thought it would be inconvenient to disclose it publicly,

452
00:40:02,950 --> 00:40:05,350
so he established this secret area.

453
00:40:05,350 --> 00:40:07,740
Isn't that right? Isn't that right?

454
00:40:07,740 --> 00:40:09,220
- How many are there? 
 - One, two...

455
00:40:09,220 --> 00:40:10,360
<i>- three, four... 
 -  Count how many there are.</i>

456
00:40:10,360 --> 00:40:11,810
- Five,  six... 
 - Are you telling the truth?

457
00:40:11,810 --> 00:40:13,730
- Seven, eight... 
 - Of course, I am!

458
00:40:13,730 --> 00:40:15,710
Our general is as kind-hearted as a Bodhisattva.

459
00:40:15,710 --> 00:40:19,190
He disregarded them being former enemies and searched for these children everywhere so they could be raised well.

460
00:40:20,020 --> 00:40:22,000
Did you miss me?

461
00:40:22,000 --> 00:40:24,160
- Pinky swear. 
 - Here, let's pinky swear.

462
00:40:24,160 --> 00:40:25,340
Pinky swear.

463
00:40:25,340 --> 00:40:26,380
I misunderstood.

464
00:40:26,380 --> 00:40:29,700
- Look at what I have in my hand. 
 - Have you all been behaving yourselves lately?

465
00:40:29,700 --> 00:40:31,650
- Does this look nice?  
 -   Yes, it does.

466
00:40:31,650 --> 00:40:33,780
Count how many there are.

467
00:40:33,780 --> 00:40:35,210
Three?

468
00:40:35,210 --> 00:40:38,110
- What are you playing? 
 - There are eight beans.

469
00:40:53,670 --> 00:40:57,310
<i>He's with me! Who dares touch him!</i>

470
00:40:57,310 --> 00:40:59,970
<i>He's with you?</i>

471
00:40:59,970 --> 00:41:02,070
<i>In any case, no one is to harm Xiao Su today.</i>

472
00:41:02,070 --> 00:41:05,170
♫ <i> The wind speaks like you </i> ♫

473
00:41:05,170 --> 00:41:08,000
<i>I made this token especially for you.</i>

474
00:41:08,000 --> 00:41:09,550
<i>You're actually using it to save his life?</i>

475
00:41:09,550 --> 00:41:12,610
♫ <i> I pause within my dream </i> ♫

476
00:41:12,610 --> 00:41:15,960
♫ <i> Counting the years of memories </i> ♫

477
00:41:17,130 --> 00:41:18,830
<i>They are here due to the goodness of the General's heart.</i>

478
00:41:18,830 --> 00:41:21,640
<i>He took in the orphaned children of the rebel army and thought it would be inconvenient to disclose it publicly,</i>

479
00:41:21,640 --> 00:41:23,410
<i>so he established this secret area.</i>

480
00:41:23,410 --> 00:41:29,640
♫ <i> Let a bottle of wine seal the story </i> ♫

481
00:41:29,640 --> 00:41:31,270
<i>Our general is as kind-hearted as a Bodhisattva.</i>

482
00:41:31,270 --> 00:41:32,840
<i>He didn't complain and searched everywhere.</i>

483
00:41:32,840 --> 00:41:34,470
<i>He disregarded them being former enemies and searched for these children everywhere so they could be raised well.</i>

